01:40:22.455 --> 01:40:24.832
- Pour the lead!
- <i>(Screaming)</i>

1181
01:40:24.916 --> 01:40:25.999
Pour it!

1182
01:40:34.634 --> 01:40:37.177
- <i>(Grunting)</i>
- <i>(Grunting)</i>

1183
01:41:18.595 --> 01:41:21.847
<i>(Laughing)</i>

1184
01:41:21.931 --> 01:41:23.432
I hate bugs!

1185
01:41:25.268 --> 01:41:27.644
<i>(Screeches)</i>

1186
01:41:36.988 --> 01:41:39.239
<i>(Hissing)</i>

1187
01:41:46.039 --> 01:41:49.082
<i>(Grunting)</i>

1188
01:41:50.084 --> 01:41:52.878
Ripley! It's burning hot!

1189
01:41:52.962 --> 01:41:56.423
Hit the sprinklers!

1190
01:41:56.508 --> 01:41:58.967
Douse the fucker!

1191
01:41:59.052 --> 01:42:01.470
<i>(Gasps)</i>

1192
01:42:07.101 --> 01:42:09.645
- <i>(Hissing)</i>
- <i>(Grunts)</i>

1193
01:42:21.449 --> 01:42:24.827
<i>(Screeching)</i>

1194
01:42:31.626 --> 01:42:33.168
Gotcha!

1195
01:42:34.254 --> 01:42:35.921
Yes!

1196
01:43:00.029 --> 01:43:01.697
<i>(Coughing)</i>

1197
01:43:05.702 --> 01:43:39.075
<i>(Gasps)</i>

1198
01:43:41.078 --> 01:43:44.623
- <i>(Ripley) Don't come any closer.</i>
- Wait. They're here to help.

1199
01:43:44.707 --> 01:43:46.249
Stay where you are!

1200
01:43:49.337 --> 01:43:52.672
- Ripley.
- Bishop.

1201
01:43:52.757 --> 01:43:55.258
- I'm here to help you.
- <i>No more bullshit.</i>

1202
01:43:55.343 --> 01:43:57.927
I just felt it move.

1203
01:43:58.012 --> 01:44:01.348
- You know who I am?
- You're a droid.

1204
01:44:01.432 --> 01:44:04.434
Same model as Bishop.
Sent by the fucking company.

1205
01:44:04.518 --> 01:44:08.563
No. I'm not the Bishop android.

1206
01:44:08.648 --> 01:44:10.899
I designed it.

1207
01:44:10.983 --> 01:44:13.485
I'm very human.

1208
01:44:13.569 --> 01:44:15.862
The company sent me here
to show you a friendly face,

1209
01:44:15.946 --> 01:44:19.699
to demonstrate how important
you are to us,

1210
01:44:19.784 --> 01:44:21.409
to me.

1211
01:44:21.494 --> 01:44:24.746
- You just want to take it back.
- We want to kill it and take you home.

1212
01:44:24.830 --> 01:44:29.334
- Bullshit.
- You're wrong. We want to help.

1213
01:44:29.418 --> 01:44:32.337
What does that mean?

1214
01:44:32.463 --> 01:44:36.633
- We're gonna take that out of you.
- <i>(Softly)</i> And keep it.

1215
01:44:36.717 --> 01:44:40.637
Can't allow it to live.
Everything we know would be in jeopardy.

1216
01:44:42.807 --> 01:44:45.058
You don't want to take it back?

1217
01:44:45.142 --> 01:44:46.935
Ripley, time is important.

1218
01:44:48.145 --> 01:44:51.940
<i>We've got a surgical bay set up
on the rescue ship. Come with me.</i>

1219
01:44:54.318 --> 01:44:56.364
You still can have a life.

1220
01:44:58.364 --> 01:44:59.364
Children...

1221
01:45:01.075 --> 01:45:04.160
<i>And most important,
you'll know it's dead.</i>

1222
01:45:04.245 --> 01:45:06.621
Let me help you.

1223
01:45:07.665 --> 01:45:10.166
What guarantee do I have...

1224
01:45:12.128 --> 01:45:13.628
once you've taken it out...

1225
01:45:15.228 --> 01:45:16.428
you'll destroy it?

1226
01:45:17.465 --> 01:45:19.300
You have to trust me.

1227
01:45:24.432 --> 01:45:27.684
Please? Trust me?

1228
01:45:32.314 --> 01:45:33.314
No.

1229
01:45:44.410 --> 01:45:47.120
- What's this gonna achieve?
- <i>(Gunshot, screams)</i>

1230
01:45:47.204 --> 01:45:50.123
- Stop!
- Ow! Oh, Jesus!

1231
01:45:50.207 --> 01:45:53.376
- <i>(Groaning)</i>
- Morse.

1232
01:45:55.838 --> 01:45:56.908
Will you help me?

1233
01:45:58.208 --> 01:46:00.008
What do you want me to do?

1234
01:46:03.137 --> 01:46:06.556
<i>(Bishop) It was a mistake!
There was no need for any of it!</i>

1235
01:46:06.640 --> 01:46:07.932
Fucking android!

1236
01:46:25.242 --> 01:46:29.704
Ripley, think of all
we could learn from it.

1237
01:46:29.789 --> 01:46:32.916
<i>It's the chance of a lifetime!</i>

1238
01:46:33.000 --> 01:46:38.004
You must let me have it!
It's a magnificent specimen!

1239
01:46:57.691 --> 01:47:00.443
<i>(Softly)</i> What are you doing?

1240
01:47:04.031 --> 01:47:06.407
No!

1241
01:47:17.795 --> 01:47:20.880
<i>(Screeching)</i>

1242
01:47:23.175 --> 01:47:25.134
<i>(Screeching continues)</i>

1243
01:48:20.900 --> 01:48:22.525
- <i>(Grunts)</i>
- <i>(Chuckles)</i>

1244
01:48:22.651 --> 01:48:26.112
- Come on, you. Get going.
- Oh, fuck you!

1245
01:48:28.574 --> 01:48:32.160
<i>(Static)</i>

1246
01:48:32.244 --> 01:48:36.581
<i>(Ripley's voice)</i>
<i>Ash, Captain Dallas are dead.</i>

1247
01:48:36.665 --> 01:48:40.460
<i>Cargo and ship destroyed.</i>

1248
01:48:40.544 --> 01:48:44.213
<i>I should reach the frontier
in about six weeks.</i>

1249
01:48:44.298 --> 01:48:47.717
<i>With a little luck,
the network will pick me up.</i>

1250
01:48:47.801 --> 01:48:49.969
<i>This is Ripley,</i>

1251
01:48:50.054 --> 01:48:53.556
<i>last survivor of the</i> Nostromo,
<i>signing off.</i>

1252
01:48:54.937 --> 01:48:56.521
<i>(Beeping)</i>